data.description: When county meets convenience! This cozy ranch home is to be enjoyed both inside and out. The inside has tasteful updates while the outside has a spacious breezeway to the 4 car garage, a spectacular covered patio with a newer hot tub, white vinyl fencing borders the paved driveway, multiple fenced pastures for your horses and other animals AND it's just a few short minutes to the freeway. property is 4 separate tax lots. buyer to do due diligence on uses.
